## 🏗️ Hygiene Principle (Lean Engineering)

- **Single Source of Truth:** each piece of information lives in one place
- **Modular:** `<folder>/index.md` in every primary module
- **Size discipline:** CLAUDE.md under 150 lines, lessons/decisions under 500 lines
- **Rotation:** when limits are hit, archive + leave a reference (never delete)
- **Audit Trail:** every routing → `tasks/audit.md`, every decision → `tasks/decisions.md`
